data.text:
Tom Cruise (born July 3, 1962) portrays IMF agent Ethan Hunt in all eight theatrical Mission: Impossible movies. He also has produced each theatrical Mission: Impossible movie so far.

Early Life[]

Cruise has starred in multiple Hollywood blockbusters, including Top Gun, The Firm, Rain Man, A Few Good Men, Jerry Maguire, Vanilla Sky, Minority Report, The Last Samurai, Collateral, War of the Worlds, Jack Reacher, Oblivion, Edge of Tomorrow co-starring with Emily Blunt, The Mummy, American Made and Top Gun: Maverick.

As of 2015, Cruise is Hollywood's 10th highest-paid actor.

Behind the Scenes[]

Cruise's cousin, William Mapother portrayed Wallis in Mission: Impossible II.
